Package: congressData
Type: Package
Title: Data Only: The Congress Data
Version: 1.0
Author: Caleb Lucas (https://caleblucas.com/)
Maintainer: Caleb Lucas <calebjlucas@gmail.com>
Description: Contains the Congress Data dataset (+ codebook) assembled by Matt Grossmann, Caleb Lucas, Josh McCrain, and Ian Ostrander. The dataset compiles approximately 800 variables concerning all US congressional districts and covers 1789-2021.
